reviewText: Our whole family really loves this series.
I hope to have the complete series, I've loved this show when it was new and I watch it now, I think damn those boys were hot, mostly Buck Cross, he was always my favorite.

The DVDs did not have the episodes that the amazon listing and DVD cover promised. The second DVD is missing "Requiem for a Hero," and has "Peacekeepers" on it, so the next disc set only has 8 episodes instead of 10.
